[@Melon yellow spot virus#Virus*] ([$MYSV#Virus*]) was previously reported from [$wax gourd#Plant*] in Thailand.
A survey of [$cantaloupe#Plant*], [$cucumber#Plant*], [$melon#Plant*], [$pumpkin#Plant*] and [$watermelon#Plant*] plants was carried out to determine if [$MYSV#Virus*] occurred more widely in [$cucurbit species#Plant*].
The survey revealed [$melon#Plant*] was mostly infected with [$MYSV#Virus*].
In addition, [$MYSV#Virus*] was detected for the first time in [$pumpkin#Plant*] in Thailand.
